{"tid":2124840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港船東會支持收緊船員換班建議","createTime":"2020-07-25T16:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T17:21:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f3723ceb87a131599d0700feb8a1223a120e88fa","tid":2124840,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T16:50:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539889-20200725.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539889-20200725.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHfaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=28e8b106\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539889-20200725.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6d584638\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539889-20200725.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港船東會發聲明，支持政府和衛生專家的建議，收緊船員換班安排。<br />\n<br />\n船東會表示，早前已經建議政府收緊對船員輪班採取的措施，包括以「測試陰性放行」取代「測試放行」，以及未來幾周只允許香港船隻和香港註冊公司安排船員輪換等，並處罰違例者採取處罰措施，希望政府採納建議，又指抗疫需要「關鍵員工」，包括海員，期望在保障本地社區安全的前提下，容許輪換持續工作多月的海員，以確保重要物資的供應鏈，例如燃料、食品和醫療用品。<br />\n<br />\n船東會又指，已要求航運公司暫緩於本港輪換非必要的船員，為期至少3星期。"},{"pid":"8b635f26b0b4944090479829475b734010ecce96","tid":2124840,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T16:53:24.000Z","msg":"［講得幾好］何柏良：海員免檢係一個持續唔堵塞既漏洞 有常識都知會出事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2124815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2124815</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"05e10c7550654c0a03cf2dee095d4a90e12d56ea","tid":2124840,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T16:56:28.000Z","msg":"支咩持政府！ 政府話唔關事呀！<br />\n政府話唔會收返呀‼️<br />\n你係要叫政府支持你個建議！"},{"pid":"790e66eec930c96aa46bcf97b95007b1d66c3dc3","tid":2124840,"uid":2682,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T17:00:06.000Z","msg":"晒氣啦, 仲有好多船排緊隊入黎做換人, 唔正式實施POLICY / REGULATION 根本無用, 唔好再用勸喻喇, 無船東會聽, 彩你都生滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363c1e9ad6fb4dd3cad7fdf11bf2c6986417a102","tid":2124840,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T17:09:32.000Z","msg":"正苦變condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaddd0b0add08ea7c8239fd6732d9f0db03d4fe9","tid":2124840,"uid":183453,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T17:15:30.000Z","msg":"新加坡有冇香港咁過分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解香港要做換班嘅地方？"},{"pid":"d0c3d032a4eade51a55bc0cbda77de5ae9c130b6","tid":2124840,"uid":1159,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T17:21:50.000Z","msg":"之前又係佢哋嗌要放寬嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}